File Name	Role	"""The One Sentence Description"""
data_loader.py	Ingestor	"Loads the CSV and warns you if the data is unbalanced (e.g., if too many people died)."
feature_engineering.py	Creator	"Brainstorms new ideas, like combining family members into one FamilySize score."
preprocessor.py	Refiner	"Fixes the ""Age"" column using Titles and converts text (Male/Female) into numbers (0/1)."
test_distribution.py	Visual Auditor	"Shows you a graph to prove your ""Age"" fixes didn't warp the reality of the data."
test_logic.py	Security Guard	Automatically stops the program if it finds a single NaN or a column it shouldn't see.
model_trainer.py	Teacher	"Trains the Random Forest ""brain"" and saves what it learned into a .pkl file."
bias_validator.py	Ethics Officer	"Checks if the model is being ""lazy"" by just guessing everyone in 3rd class dies."
predict.py	Messenger	"Takes the finalized ""brain"" and applies it to the test.csv to get your final answers."
main.py	Conductor	The master script that tells all the other files when it's their turn to run.
